title: Caught Offside: Nervous flight attendant
description:
Well, if you were looking for some USMNT reassurance, you didn't get it on this day. We break down another uninspiring performance from the boys in black and blue and sort through the good and the bad as Qatar beckons. Plus: Harry Magiure does his best "Unlucky Alf" impression and JJ does his best Michael Sheen impression.
